{"tid":1700880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【10秒讀懂】點解「前線無罪論」會搞死場運動？","createTime":"2019-11-08T17:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T01:40:55.000Z","uid":53610,"like":47,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"7057f35735547a1911d2db6837e1b5f754cbb816","tid":1700880,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"一個好簡單的博弈推論<br />\n<br />\n以TVB前線為例，喺「前線無罪論」TVB篇中主要有三個角色<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者</span>、<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">TVB前線</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB高層</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三者互相影響，最後作出唔同的行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者</span></span><br />\n1. 知道TVB造假新聞<br />\n1. 知道TVB前線有黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 唔會對TVB前線落手</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">TVB前線</span></span><br />\n1. 幫TVB造假新聞<br />\n2. 知道抗爭者唔會對自己落手<br />\n2. 被TVB高層拖壓<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 為生計繼續幫TVB造假新聞</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB高層</span></span><br />\n1. 造假新聞<br />\n1. 知道TVB前線有黃<br />\n2. 對前線拖壓<br />\n2. 知道抗爭者唔會對TVB前線落手<br />\n3. 知道TVB前線會繼續配合自己造假新聞<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 繼續造假新聞</span><br />\n<br />\n結果就係，抗爭者冇有效打擊TVB高層的方法，同時秉持前線無罪論唔對TVB前線落手<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，TVB前線同TVB高層就繼續夾手夾腳造緊假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後結束呢個回合，有冇發現<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第一局TVB係贏到開巷！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係咪好神奇呢？<br />\n明明做緊個行動好似幾啱咁，但最後成個棋局就走向對自己不利的方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所謂前線就好比一粒棋，你以為你同佢都係「車」，所以大家係同夥，點知睇真啲，原來係對家隻「車」嚟<br />\n<br />\n你唔食佢，對家就用依粒棋食埋你隻「車」，你最後為咗個以為係手足的敵人，輸咗成盤棋<br />\n<br />\n不過好彩，盤棋係三局兩勝<br />\n依家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知道第二局要點捉未？</span></span>"},{"pid":"72b16dd513c99657d2310507f23baee5639273a0","tid":1700880,"uid":37869,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:32:15.000Z","msg":"所以幫助政權傷害香港人的人都係抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535a1088e5b0c11b294d30b486cfe18fa2bf4ae8","tid":1700880,"uid":4783,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:33:45.000Z","msg":"又黎中計黨<br />\ntvb又贏<br />\n港共又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0cd561b7a17f68e8df6903ebdb69d187064280e","tid":1700880,"uid":304726,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:34:49.000Z","msg":"仲以為你講手足，睇真啲先知係講緊tvb嘅前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d31733501dcf1c6ff5764f7ecf25061bb8250c5","tid":1700880,"uid":262116,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7057f35735547a1911d2db6837e1b5f754cbb816","tid":1700880,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"一個好簡單的博弈推論<br />\n<br />\n以TVB前線為例，喺「前線無罪論」TVB篇中主要有三個角色<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者</span>、<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">TVB前線</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB高層</span></span><br />\n<br />\n三者互相影響，最後作出唔同的行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗爭者</span></span><br />\n1. 知道TVB造假新聞<br />\n1. 知道TVB前線有黃<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 唔會對TVB前線落手</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">TVB前線</span></span><br />\n1. 幫TVB造假新聞<br />\n2. 知道抗爭者唔會對自己落手<br />\n2. 被TVB高層拖壓<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3. 為生計繼續幫TVB造假新聞</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB高層</span></span><br />\n1. 造假新聞<br />\n1. 知道TVB前線有黃<br />\n2. 對前線拖壓<br />\n2. 知道抗爭者唔會對TVB前線落手<br />\n3. 知道TVB前線會繼續配合自己造假新聞<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">4. 繼續造假新聞</span><br />\n<